<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="79">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wei-lan-tian-kong-43" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wei-lan-tian-kong-43" class="zg-link" title="蔚蓝天空">蔚蓝天空</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yi-wen-47" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yi-wen-47" class="zg-link" title="汉文">汉文</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yao-qing-shu" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yao-qing-shu" class="zg-link" title="坠吼是窝">坠吼是窝</a></span>
