<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$zhang-zhen-guang-79" href="/people/zhang-zhen-guang-79">张臻光</a>，<strong title="这个家伙太懒，什么也没留下……" class="zu-question-my-bio">这个家伙太懒，什么也没留下……</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="4">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhu-rui-jie" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhu-rui-jie" class="zg-link" title="Zhu Roger">Zhu Roger</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$compiler" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/compiler" class="zg-link" title="浪客">浪客</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户</span>
